<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="view/macro:page/freeform" 
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>
    <div metal:fill-slot="main">
      <h1>Help improve Launchpad</h1>
      <p>
        We are always working to improve Launchpad, and regularly make new
        features and bugfixes available on our live servers. If you have
        suggestions for how we can make Launchpad better, we want to hear them.
      </p>
      <p>
        There are three main ways to tell us about your idea:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Chat with us:</strong> if you want to discuss your
            suggestion with a member of the Launchpad team, visit us in
            <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#launchpad">
            <code>#launchpad</code> on <code>irc.freenode.net</code></a>
            or email <a
            href="http://lists.canonical.com/mailman/listinfo/launchpad-users">
            the Launchpad users mailing list</a>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Report a bug:</strong> if you&#8217;ve found a bug in
            Launchpad, first check to see if it&#8217;s already been reported
            in our <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/launchpad-project/">bug
            tracker</a>.
            If it hasn&#8217;t, create a new report in the bug tracker for the
            Launchpad application you were using:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/malone/">Bug Tracker</a>
              (also formerly called Malone)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/rosetta/">Translations</a>
              (also formerly called Rosetta)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/blueprint/">Blueprints</a>
              (for creating and tracking specifications)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/soyuz/">Distribution
              Management</a>
              (managing packages and builds, also called Soyuz)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/launchpad-bazaar/">Code</a>
              (hosting and managing Bazaar branches)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/launchpad-answers/">Answer
              Tracker</a>
              (for seeking and offering help)
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://bugs.launchpad.net/launchpad/">any other
              aspect of Launchpad</a>.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Write a blueprint:</strong> if you have an idea for a new
            feature,
            <a href="https://blueprints.launchpad.net/launchpad-project/"
            >search the Blueprint Tracker</a> to see if it has already been
            planned or discussed.
            If not, write up a summary and discuss it with the Launchpad team
            on IRC.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Thanks for helping us make Launchpad a great place to develop software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
